name: FuzzTerminal // Free Live
description:
It's a psychedelic-garagerock orchestra for yer bleeding ears!
So far this quintet have resealed two singles.
Their debutalbum is due autumn 2026.

Guitar, modular synth, harmony vocal — Espen Paulsen
Guitar — Kim-Frode Wøhni
Bass, vocals — Jørund Vålandsmyr
Percussion, electronics, synth — Espen Skjørdal
Drums — Daniel Horn
